name: CompositeMapTest
description: Unit tests for the CompositeMap class, which is part of the Apache Commons Collections library.

test_cases.name: testAddComposited
test_cases.description: Tests the addition of composited maps to a CompositeMap and checks for key presence.

test_cases.name: testGet
test_cases.description: Tests the retrieval of values from a CompositeMap.

test_cases.name: testPut
test_cases.description: Tests the insertion of a key-value pair into a CompositeMap using a custom MapMutator.

test_cases.name: testPutAll
associated_methods: CompositeMap.MapMutator.putAll(CompositeMap<K, V>, Map<K, V>[], Map<? extends K, ? extends V>)
test_cases.description: Tests the insertion of all key-value pairs from a map into a CompositeMap using a custom MapMutator.

test_cases.name: testRemoveComposited
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of composited maps from a CompositeMap and checks for key presence.

test_cases.name: testRemoveFromComposited
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of a key-value pair from a composited map within a CompositeMap.

test_cases.name: testRemoveFromUnderlying
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of a key-value pair from an underlying map within a CompositeMap.

test_cases.name: testResolveCollision
primary_tested: CompositeMap.MapMutator.resolveCollision(CompositeMap<K, V>, Map<K, V>, Map<K, V>, Collection<K>)
test_cases.description: Tests the resolution of key collisions in a CompositeMap using a custom MapMutator.
